quran[16{c,v,t}:
7,105,mujh par wajib hai ke khuda ki taraf se jo kuch kahoon sach hi kahoon. mein tumahray paas tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishani le kar aaya hon. so bani Israel ko mere sath jaane ki rukhsat day degiye
7,106,firaon ne kaha agar tum nishani le kar aeye ho to agar sachey ho to lao ( dikhao )
7,107,moose ne apni laathi ( zameen par ) daal di to woh isi waqt Sarih asdeha ( hogaya )
7,108,aur apna haath bahar nikala to isi dam dekhnay walon ki nigahon mein safaid Buraq ( tha )
7,109,to qoum firaon mein jo sardar they woh kehnay lagey ke yeh bara allama jadugar hai
7,110,is ka iradah yeh hai ke tum ko tumahray malik se nikaal day. bhala tumharikiya Salah hai ?
7,111,unhon ne ( firaon se ) kaha ke fi al haal moose aur is ke bhai ke muamlay ko maaf rakhiye aur shehron mein naqeeb rawana kar degiye
7,112,ke tamam maahirgado garon ko aap ke paas le ayen
7,113,( chunancha aisa hikiya gaya ) aur jadugar firaon ke paas aa Pehncahy aur kehnay lagey ke agar hum jeet gay to hamein sila ataakiya jaye
7,114,( firaon ne ) kaha haan ( zaroor ) aur ( is ke ilawa ) tum muqarabon mein daakhil karliye jao ge
7,115,( jab fariqain rozِ muqarara par jama hue to ) gado garonne kaha ke moose ya to tum ( jaadoo ki cheez ) daalo ya hum daaltay hain
7,116,( moose ne ) kaha tum hi daalo. jab unhon ne ( jaadoo ki cheezein ) dalain to logon ki aankhon par jaadoo kardiya ( yani nzrbndi kar di ) aur ( lathyon aur rassiyon ke saanp bana bana kar ) inhen dara diya aur bohat bara jaadoo dekhaya
7,117,( is waqt ) hum ne moose ki taraf wahi bhaije ke tum bhi apni laathi daal do. woh foran ( saanp ban kar ) gado garonke banaye hue saanpon ko ( aik aik karkay ) nigal jaye gi
7,118,"( phir ) to haq saabit hogaya aur jo kuch fravni karte they, baatil hogaya"
7,119,aur woh maghloob hogaye aur zaleel hokar reh gay
7,120,( yeh kefiyat dekh kar ) jadugar sjday mein gir parre
